name: CI Global REIT Private Pool
longDescription: The CI Global REIT Private Pool seeks to provide regular income and capital appreciation. The fund investing primarily in real estate income trusts (REITs) and equity securities of corporations participating in the residential and commercial real estate sector located anywhere in the world..
